OL,3,CWoman says endometriosis 'stole her
OL,4,Clife' after years of pain without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FA woman from Belfast has said a
OL,8,Fdebilitating condition has "stolen her
OL,9,Flife" after years of living in pain
OL,10,Fwithout answers.
OL,12,FEndometriosis affects around one in
OL,13,Ften women, yet diagnosis can take up
OL,14,Fto a decade.
OL,16,FCampaigners are now calling for urgent
OL,17,Faction to cut waiting times and
OL,18,Fimprove care.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@EO]
