OL,3,CWoman says endometriosis 'stole her
OL,4,Clife' after years of pain without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FKerry Ann Smith, 47, says her life
OL,8,Flooks very different from what she
OL,9,Fonce imagined.
OL,11,FPreviously working full-time, she now
OL,12,Fstruggles to get through each day due
OL,13,Fto chronic pain and exhaustion.
OL,15,FEndometriosis is a condition where
OL,16,Ftissue similar to the lining of the
OL,17,Fwomb grows elsewhere in the body,
OL,18,Fcausing severe pain, fatigue and, in
OL,19,Fsome cases, infertility. Like many
OL,20,Fwomen, Kerry Ann faced a long wait
OL,21,Fbefore finally receiving a diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
