FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1775848268
OL,3,CWoman says endometriosis 'stole her
OL,4,Clife' after years of pain without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FOn average, it takes between eight and
OL,8,Ften years to diagnose the condition in
OL,9,Fthe UK delays campaigners say are
OL,10,Fleaving women to suffer in silence.
OL,12,FA parliamentary petition is now
OL,13,Fcalling for change, including a target
OL,14,Fof diagnosing the condition within six
OL,15,Fmonths and mandatory training for GPs
OL,16,Fto better recognise symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
