OL,3,CWoman says endometriosis 'stole her
OL,4,Clife' after years of pain without
OL,5,Canswers
OL,7,FBehind the petition is nurse Liz
OL,8,FWenden-Kerr, who says Northern Ireland
OL,9,Furgently needs a dedicated women's
OL,10,Fhealth strategy. She says too many
OL,11,Fpatients are being left in
OL,12,Fdebilitating pain for years without
OL,13,Fproper support or treatment.
OL,15,FKerry Ann is speaking out to raise
OL,16,Fawareness and encourage other women
OL,17,Fnot to ignore their symptoms.
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
